Here’s what we’re planning in upcoming releases:

v1.0
Basic NLP chatbot with context.
Minimal predictive analytics module.
Code intelligence (experimental).
v1.1
Web-based Explainability Dashboard.
Deeper GitHub integration (automated PR reviews).
Plugin system foundation for community contributions.
v2.0
Project Management Insights: advanced sprint predictions, resource planning.
Full-blown plugin ecosystem with computer vision add-ons.
Extended multi-lingual support in NLP.
